'''''andave''''' is a [[Quenya]] adverb meaning "long"<ref>{{L|230}}</ref><ref name=Cormallen>{{RK|Cormallen}}</ref> or "at great length".<ref>{{PE|17}}, p. 102</ref> It was apparently derived from the adjective ''[[anda]]''.<ref>[http://folk.uib.no/hnohf/quen-eng.htm Quettaparma Quenyallo] (accessed 28 November 2010)</ref>

==Examples==
* ''Andave laituvalmet!'' "Praise them for a long time!"<ref name=Cormallen/>

